On today’s summit, Syria delegate angrily rebuked delegates of America, England, and France, for the draft resolution condemning the use of force against Syria was not adopted. He said that they had waged a war of terrorism in Syria for seven years.   
Xinhua News Agency thinks delegates of America, England, and France should make a response to explain their doings. They should know that they had bring war and fear to citizens of Syria.
